I got the following Warning in the Starter UI:

Failed to load conformance statement, error was: ca.uhn.fhir.rest.client.exceptions.FhirClientConnectionException: Failed to parse response from server when performing GET to URL http://MyIPString:8080/fhir/metadata?_pretty=true - java.net.SocketTimeoutException: Read timed out
In most cases, this warning will appear. In a few cases, everything is Okay.
